media$description.$t: This video is made for Taylor Swift, Ellen DeGeneres, and anyone and everyone who cares about music and the Deaf Community.  It explains why Equal Access to Music for Deaf/HoH people is important, and explains why I do what I do.  I hope to get Taylor or Ellen to watch the video and respond before I meet them both on Thursday, October 18th.  Please share with anyone and everyone!! Deaf and Hard of Hearing people deserve the right to access to music - same as we do! Let's make it happen!

"Do I," by Luke Bryan, expressed in American Sign Language by Ally.

When searching for YouTube vids, be sure to take notice of if it is REALLY ASL, or if it's SEE/English that is mislabeled.. There are LOTS of SEE/English YouTubers out there. If you're wanting TRUE ASL, take caution..

Add me as a fan on Facebook!: http://www.facebook.com/pages/Ally-ASL/207129801391?ref=ts
Follow me on Twitter!: https://twitter.com/allyasl

Lyrics & GLOSS (for ASL):
Baby, what are we becoming
HEY, OUR LOVE RELATIONSHIP PAST, PROGRESS CHANGE?
It feels just like we're always running
FEELS LIKE ALWAYS AVOID. OBLIVIOUS.
Rolling through the motions everyday
EVERYDAY SAME-SAME LAID-BACK BORING.
I can lean in to hold you, or act like I don't even know you
CAN I LEAN-IN HOLD-YOU.  OR.  ACT IGNORE, DON'T-CARE.
Seems like you could care less either way
EITHER-OR, YOU DON'T-CARE.  
What happened to that girl I used to know
LOOKING BACK, YOU, PROGRESS-TIME YOU CHANGE. HAPPEN WHAT?
I just want us back to the way we were before
YOU-AND-I RELATIONSHIP PAST. NOW, I WANT AGAIN!

Do I turn you on at all when I kiss you baby,
HAPPEN KISS-YOU, YOU EXCITED????
Does the sight of me wanting you drive you crazy,
ME WANTWANTWANT YOU, THAT, EXCITE YOU????
Do I have your love? Am I still enough?
YOUR HEART, HAVE? I STILL ENOUGH?
Tell me don't I, or tell me do I baby
TELL-ME. NO? OR YES? WHICH?
Give you everything that you ever wanted
EVERYTHING YOU WANT, I GIVEGIVEGIVE, RIGHT?
Would you rather just turn away and leave me lonely?
YOU PREFER WALK-AWAY, LEAVE-ME LONELY?
Do I just need to give up and get on with my life
I NEED GIVE-UP; MY LIFE CONTINUE ALONE? 
Baby, do I
BABY, DO I?

Remember when we didn't have nothing
REMEMBER PAST. WE HAVE NOTHING. ZERO.
But a perfect simple kind of loving
BUT, HAVE LOVE. PERFECT.
Baby those sure were the days
LOOKING BACK, CHERISH.
There was a time our love ran wild and free
IN-THE-PAST, OUR LOVE NEW EXCITING FRESH.
But now I'm second guessing everything I see
BUT NOW, CONFUSED.  PERPLEXED.

Do I turn you on at all when I kiss you baby,
HAPPEN KISS-YOU, YOU EXCITED????
Does the sight of me wanting you drive you crazy,
ME WANTWANTWANT YOU, THAT, EXCITE YOU????
Do I have your love? Am I still enough?
YOUR HEART, HAVE? I STILL ENOUGH?
Tell me don't I, or tell me do I baby
TELL-ME. NO? OR YES? WHICH?
Give you everything that you ever wanted
EVERYTHING YOU WANT, I GIVEGIVEGIVE, RIGHT?
Would you rather just turn away and leave me lonely?
YOU PREFER WALK-AWAY, LEAVE-ME LONELY?
Do I just need to give up and get on with my life
I NEED GIVE-UP; MY LIFE CONTINUE ALONE? 
Baby, do I
BABY, DO I?

Still give you what you need
YOU SATISFY STILL?
Still take your breath away
TAKE-YOUR-BREATH-AWAY STILL?
Or light up the spark way down deep, baby do I
INSPIRE PEP-UP? BABY, DO I?

Do I turn you on at all when I kiss you baby,
HAPPEN KISS-YOU, YOU EXCITED????
Does the sight of me wanting you drive you crazy,
ME WANTWANTWANT YOU, THAT, EXCITE YOU????
Do I have your love? Am I still enough?
YOUR HEART, HAVE? I STILL ENOUGH?
Tell me don't I, or tell me do I baby
TELL-ME. NO? OR YES? WHICH?
Give you everything that you ever wanted
EVERYTHING YOU WANT, I GIVEGIVEGIVE, RIGHT?
Would you rather just turn away and leave me lonely?
YOU PREFER WALK-AWAY, LEAVE-ME LONELY?
Do I just need to give up and get on with my life
I NEED GIVE-UP; MY LIFE CONTINUE ALONE? 
Tell me baby do I get one more try
TELL ME. GIVE ONE MORE TRY? 
Do I, baby do I
DO I PLEASE?  BABY, DO I?

"Do I" by Luke Bryan, expressed in American Sign Language (and SEE/English).  SEE is Signing Exact English, and I did my best to try and express that in the corner of this video.  I wanted to show the differences between ASL and SEE/English.  There is a HUGEEEE difference, and hopefully this helps to see that.  SEE and English SL are NOT languages. ASL, however, IS a language! Enjoy!

media$description.$t:
Live, from the Keith Wann show, is "Fireflies" by Owl City; performed by Ally in American Sign Language. :)

Thanks to Mina Gordon and Keith Wann for inviting and allowing me to perform! What an opportunity! Also, thanks to Kristen (Zadinak)  for the recording.  I have a little better version that I'll upload as soon as I get on DVD, but for now this one will suffice. :) THANKS TO ALL THE YT'ERS THAT CAME OUT TO WATCH AND SUPPORT ME! I LOVE ALL OF YOU!! :)

Add yourself as a "fan" on my Facebook Fan Page! :)
http://www.facebook.com/pages/Ally-ASL/207129801391?ref=search&sid=9220012.397417773..1

Lyrics & GLOSS:
You would not believe your eyes, if ten million fireflies lit up the world as I fell asleep.
SUPPOSE HAPPEN FALL ASLEEP. 10 MILLION LIGHT BUGS SPREAD-OUT. YOU AMAZE WILL.
Cause they fill the open air and leave teardrops everywhere. You'd think me rude but I would just stand and stare. 
WHY? EVERYWHERE SPREAD-OUT. LIGHT TEARS DROP DROP DROP. STARE STARE. RUDE I? NO NO. ENTHRALLED. JAW-DROPS.

I'd like to make myself believe that planet earth turns slowly.
BELIEVE MYSELF WANT. EARTH PEOPLE LAID-BACK SLOW. BUSY BUSY PUSH-AWAY.
Its hard to say that I'd rather stay awake when I'm asleep. Cause everything is never as it seems. 
SUPPOSE I ASLEEP. PREFER AWAKE? NO. WHY? DREAM DREAM. POP DREAM.

Cause I'd Get A Thousand Hugs, From Ten Thousand Lightning Bugs As They Tried To Teach Me How To Dance
FIREFLIES MANY MANY INSPIRE-ON-ARMS ME. DANCE THEY TRY TEACH ME.  
A Foxtrot Above My head A Sockhop Beneath My Bed A Disco Ball Is Just hanging By A thread
LOOK-UP FOXTROT DANCE DANCE.  BED, LOOK-DOWN SOCKHOP DANCE. THREAD FS:DISCO BALL SPARKLY-TURN 

I'd like to make myself believe that planet earth turns slowly.
BELIEVE MYSELF WANT. EARTH PEOPLE LAID-BACK SLOW. BUSY BUSY PUSH-AWAY.
Its hard to say that I'd rather stay awake when I'm asleep. Cause everything is never as it seems. When I Fall Asleep
SUPPOSE I ASLEEP. PREFER AWAKE? NO. WHY? I SLEEP. DREAM DREAM. POP DREAM.

Leave My Door Open Just A crack, Please Take Me Away From Here.
DOOR OPEN LITTLE-BIT HAVE-TO. WHY? HAPPEN ESCAPE CAN.
Cause I Feel Like Such An Insomniac Please Take Me Away From Here
WHY? FEEL LIKE SLEEP CANT I. SLEEP REALLY WANT.
Why Do I Tire Of Counting Sheep, Please Take Me Away From Here.
TRY SHEEP COUNT. SICK-OF-IT, FED-UP. HOPE SLEEP SOON. 
When I'm far Too Tired To Fall Asleep
EXHAUSTED(WORN-OUT) BUT SLEEP CANT. ALL-NIGHT TOSS-AND-TURN.

To Ten Million Fireflies, I'm Weird Cause I Hate Goodbyes
FIREFLIES MANY ALL-OVER. STRANGE ME. WHY? LEAVE LEAVE DISAPPEAR, DONT-LIKE.
I Got Misty Eyes As They Said Farewell
THEY SAY BYE BYE. I MISTY-EYED. CRY CRY.
But I'll Know Where Several Are If My Dreams Get Real Bizzare Cause I Saved A Few And I Keep Them In A Jar
BUT. SUPPOSE DREAM [TURNS BAD  USE FACIALS] PUSH AWAY, FINE WILL.  WHY? FIREFLIES HAVE IN JAR. (OPEN JAR)  

I'd like to make myself believe that planet earth turns slowly.
BELIEVE MYSELF WANT. EARTH PEOPLE LAID-BACK SLOW. BUSY BUSY PUSH-AWAY.
Its hard to say that I'd rather stay awake when I'm asleep. Cause everything is never as it seems. When I Fall Asleep
SUPPOSE ASLEEP. PREFER AWAKE? NO. WHY? SLEEP I. DREAM DREAM. POP DREAM.

I'd like to make myself believe that planet earth turns slowly.
BELIEVE MYSELF WANT. EARTH PEOPLE LAID-BACK SLOW. BUSY BUSY PUSH-AWAY.
Its hard to say that I'd rather stay awake when I'm asleep. Cause everything is never as it seems. When I Fall Asleep
SUPPOSE ASLEEP. PREFER AWAKE? NO. WHY? SLEEP I. DREAM DREAM. POP DREAM.

I'd Like To make Myself Believe That Planet earth Turns Slowly
BELIEVE MYSELF WANT. EARTH PEOPLE LAID-BACK SLOW. BUSY BUSY PUSH-AWAY.
It's Hard To Say I'd Rather Stay Awake When I'm Asleep
SUPPOSE ASLEEP. PREFER AWAKE? NO. WHY?
Because My Dreams Are Bursting At The Seams
DREAM. DREAM. DREAM. BIG-DREAM.

A Foxtrot Above My head A Sockhop Beneath My Bed A Disco Ball Is Just hanging By A thread
LOOK-UP FOXTROT DANCE DANCE.  BED, LOOK-DOWN SOCKHOP DANCE. THREAD FS:DISCO BALL SPARKLY-TURN

Why Do I Tire Of Counting Sheep, Please Take Me Away From Here.
TRY SHEEP COUNT. SICK-OF-IT, FED-UP. HOPE SLEEP SOON. 
When I'm far Too Tired To Fall Asleep
EXHAUSTED(WORN-OUT) BUT SLEEP CANT. ALL-NIGHT TOSS-AND-TURN.

To Ten Million Fireflies, I'm Weird Cause I Hate Goodbyes
FIREFLIES MANY ALL-OVER. STRANGE ME. WHY? LEAVE LEAVE DISAPPEAR, DONT-LIKE.
I Got Misty Eyes As They Said Farewell
THEY SAY BYE BYE. I MISTY-EYED. CRY CRY.
But I'll Know Where Several Are If My Dreams Get Real Bizzare Cause I Saved A Few And I Keep Them In A Jar
BUT. SUPPOSE DREAM [TURNS BAD  USE FACIALS] PUSH AWAY, FINE WILL.  WHY? FIREFLIES HAVE IN JAR. (OPEN JAR)

BELIEVE MYSELF WANT. EARTH PEOPLE LAID-BACK SLOW. BUSY BUSY PUSH-AWAY.
It's Hard To Say I'd Rather Stay Awake When I'm Asleep
SUPPOSE ASLEEP. PREFER AWAKE? NO. WHY?
Because My Dreams Are Bursting At The Seams
DREAM. DREAM. DREAM. BIG-DREAM.

"Should've Said No" by Taylor Swift, expressed in American Sign Language.

Requested By:
iluvkyothecat83
xblckxangelx
Davison
Thanks for requesting and watching! Enjoy!

ALSO! Add yourself as a FAN on my Facebook Fan Page! 
http://www.facebook.com/pages/Ally-ASL/207129801391
(or search Ally ASL!)

Lyrics:
It's strange to think the songs we used to sing,
The smiles, the flowers, everything,
Is gone.
Yesterday I found out about you,
Even now just looking at you,
Feels wrong.
You say, that you'd take it all back,
Given one chance, it was a moment of weakness,
And you said yes

You should've said no,
You should've gone home,
You should have thought twice before you let it all go.
You should've known that word 'bout what you did with her'd, get back to me.
And I should've been there, in the back of your mind,
Shouldn't be asking myself why,
You shouldn't be begging for forgivness at my feet,
You should've said no
Baby and you might still have me.

You can see that I've been cryin',
Baby you know all the right things,
To say.
But do you, honestly,
Expect me, to believe,
We could ever be the same.
You say, that the past is the past,
You need one chance, it was a moment of weakness,
And you said yes

You should've said no,
You should've gone home,
You should have thought twice before you let it all go.
You should've known that word 'bout what you did with her'd, get back to me.
And I should've been there, in the back of your mind
Shouldn't be asking myself why,
You shouldn't be begging for forgiveness at my feet,
You should've said no
Baby and you might still have me..

I can't resist,
Before you go tell me this,
Was it worth it,
Was she worth this.

No, no, no, no

You should've said no,
You should've gone home,
You should have thought twice before you let it all go.
You should've known that word 'bout what you did with her'd, get back to me.
And I should've been there, in the back of your mind
Shouldn't be asking myself why,
You shouldn't be begging for forgiveness at my feet,
You should've said no
Baby and you might still have me..

media$description.$t:
"Unbeautiful" by Lesley Roy, expressed in American Sign Language.
THIS WAS DONE COMPLETELY COLD. NO PRACTICE AT ALL. SO BE LENIANT! haha

All copyrights belong to their owner, Lesley Roy, and her record company. I am not claiming anything.

Lyrics:
Don't hang up, can't we talk
So confused it's like I'm lost
What went wrong, what made you go
Don't pretend you don't know
This is me I'm unchangable

When did we fall apart
Or did you lie from the start
When you said, it's only you
I was blind, such a fool
Thinking we were unbreakable

[Chorus]
It was you and me, against the world
And you promised me forever more
Was it something that I said
Was it something that I did
Cause I gotta know what made me unbeautiful

[Verse 2]
I've been told what's done is done
To let it go and carry on
Deep inside I know that's true
I'm stuck in time, stuck on you
When We were still untouchable

[Chorus]
It was you and me, against the world
And you promised me forever more
Was it something that I said
Was it something that I did
Cause I gotta know what made me unbeautiful

[Bridge]
Wake up, wake up, wake up, wake up
Cause I'm only dreaming
Get out, get out, get out, get out
Get out of my head now
Because we're much better altogether
Can't let go

[Chorus] x2
It was you and me, against the world
And you promised me forever more
Was it something that I said
Was it something that I did
Cause I gotta know what made me unbeautiful

It was you and me, against the world
And you promised me forever more
Was it something that I said
Was it something that I did
Cause I gotta know what made me unbeautiful

... Made me unbeautiful
